    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts up reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, offering a dependable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and structurally sound. It has been regularly serviced, with all major systems functioning as expected, making it a solid choice for anyone seeking a reliable and honest pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 33500.0,
